{"tid":414351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我好興奮啊」宅男興奮哥後來怎麼了？","createTime":"2017-09-26T07:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T08:23:11.000Z","uid":32938,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd6d741c959c29b502c62fc737e282fc1f41f4d","tid":414351,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170922/640_ffb100ae7099df4d54d6e26852a4158b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170922%2F640_ffb100ae7099df4d54d6e26852a4158b.jpg&h=a1caa8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在網路上常見的「我好興奮啊！」的畫面截圖，被稱為肥宅之光的興奮哥背後有著勵志的奮鬥史，從熱愛少女偶像，到如今他以自己對少女偶像的熱情與研究，而開啟了人生新的一條道路，他的故事是這樣的......<br />\n<br />\n興奮哥　31歲　新北市　藝文服務業<br />\n六年前日本少女偶像AKB48來台，新聞台拍到我激動地說「我好興奮啊」的畫面，那之後大家都叫我「興奮哥」，一直到現在。其實我本來對偶像沒有接觸，有次出差在秋葉原看到哪裡都是少女偶像的歌跟影片，很洗腦，不知不覺就一直看下去，成員來了當然也要去朝聖。<br />\n<br />\n會被拍到是因為氣氛使然，情緒特別激昂。但那圖出來以後，有人講我「噁宅」、「肥宅」、「就是有你這樣的人，大家才會看不起喜歡偶像的人」。我會覺得被曲解，但更多是無能為力，就算只是想直白表達，還是被看成一個怪胎、畸形。<br />\n<br />\n我常把偶像現場比喻成一個完美的共產社會。大家進了場，不管你是社長或雜工、有錢人或窮人，只要換上同一件T恤，拿同樣的螢光棒跟毛巾，大家都是一樣的，沒有階級，一起看著同一個方向。這些偶像會用推特跟社群軟體，到現場也可以碰面，跟她講話甚至會回覆你，我覺得就像投接球，很有親近感。<br />\n<br />\n工作領到薪水，我會去日本參加Live，只要買周邊就可以跟少女們合照、握手聊天，一年累積下來三、四十場，每次去二十萬日幣現金就不見了。爸媽多少會念，覺得玩物喪志，台灣家長最喜歡講：「這些東西能換錢嗎？能當飯吃嗎？」後來我不想靠家裡在中國的事業，回台灣找工作，但履歷投了上百封沒人要我，我決定做自己喜歡的事，研究偶像團。因為常跑日本現場，認識的製作人對我印象深刻，今年終於接到偶像來台表演的案子，沒想到我現在真的靠這個吃飯。<br />\n<br />\n我一直覺得我是個結不了婚的人，家人雖然會講會念，但他們看我的樣子應該也知道強求不來。看到自己那張興奮照，我不覺得遺憾或後悔，那就是我的legacy。我相信人生在世就是多少留下一點爪痕，這樣，至少還可以說自己有活過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170922/1205994/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170922%2F1205994%2F&d=hq1Tv1DQFqCq6TPm3S9dwv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d7d694b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170922/1205994/</a>"},{"pid":"473323bf03ab8bee4cf3d54963b6268f588fba02","tid":414351,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1338/1338728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1338%2F1338728.jpg&h=8191b732&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db785cd5c964b80da579af3bc5214c12bbaf30bf","tid":414351,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"社會標籤<br />\n但人就是有各式各樣<br />\n不會改變自己去迎合他人<br />\n我尊敬佢<br />\n最少佢冇偷呃拐騙"},{"pid":"56f4f4374746cb13fb7be6b1319d69288468d7b8","tid":414351,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"成功唔到 只少做到自己想做既野"},{"pid":"6abbe8b5176b8a62efd6fb1b4feca65cd6b231e4","tid":414351,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"興奮哥先係我真正嘅idol<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2566325cde850627bf2bcaf282f2ae8b047e2cc3","tid":414351,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/1f/ITsjzHNhbszQF.gif/revision/latest?cb=20120710073220\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F1f%2FITsjzHNhbszQF.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120710073220&h=15d93998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港代表"},{"pid":"986296ca01fa93ac06c24c42244bb0699b840ff2","tid":414351,"uid":8598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社會標籤<br />\n但人就是有各式各樣<br />\n不會改變自己去迎合他人<br />\n我尊敬佢<br />\n最少佢冇偷呃拐騙</blockquote><br />\n啱呀，做人就係要忠於自己，敢愛敢恨"},{"pid":"45688747e58778ab33f2a72c53c41ec3aac083d7","tid":414351,"uid":13856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"咁多飛機杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca40bb52fe6b6c18c1807104106b681369ac63e","tid":414351,"uid":82528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"飛機杯同akb有咩關係？"},{"pid":"0f65b27f7304fd74807dad7434da951852afcecc","tid":414351,"uid":67331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"一年累積下來三、四十場，每次去二十萬日幣現金就不見了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n14000港紙 X 35 = 49萬港紙一年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff41757d005dc6daf748a8b7fd380784d1369ab","tid":414351,"uid":11017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一年累積下來三、四十場，每次去二十萬日幣現金就不見了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n14000港紙 X 35 = 49萬港紙一年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗佢意思係一年累積下來三、四十場&quot;LIVE&quot;<br />\n每次去&quot;日本&quot;二十萬日幣現金就不見了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一場洗到20萬都幾勁"}]}